<h2>High C Advisors</h2>
<p>
	<ul>
		<li>
		Interact with client in an objective, fact-based, and task-oriented manner.
		<li>
		Present information filled with details, relying on charts, graphs, and written 
		material.
		<li>
		Avoid small talk unless client initiates.
		<li>
		May seem detached with regard to clients’ personal lives and families.
		<li>
		Create credibility through self-discipline, dedication, accuracy, and technical 
		expertise.
		<li>
		Express little emotion, personal opinions, or intuitive feelings in 
		discussions.
		<LI>
			May overwhelm with information, both orally and in writing.</LI>
	</ul>
